    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings to be found. The original alloy wheels are pristine, completely free of curb rash, and wrapped in high-performance tires. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury, featuring premium leather upholstery that remains taut and free of any wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full, documented service history exclusively from authorized specialists. It drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new machine. Included in the sale are both original keys, the factory tool kit, and all original manuals in their leather binder. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a flawless, investment-grade example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
