      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard and preserved in showroom condition. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetic integrity and mechanical precision, representing the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the lustrous exterior finish, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of distinguished caliber.",
      "price": 44900.0,
